= outfit( set1, ..., setN ) =

Matches items in sets from outfit mods, eg Outfitter, ClosetGnome, ItemRack

== Alias ==
`uselvl()`

== Arguments ==

  * min = minimum level to search for
  * max = maximum level to search for

== Remarks ==
  * the level can be found on the debug info menu for that item (or in the tooltip)
  * when only the min argument is passed then the function checks for an exact level match 

== Examples ==

`ireq( 70 )`

`ireq( 61-69 )`
